quran[54]{c,v,t}:
  20,1,Twa Ha
  20,2,Asiyehliselanga phansi kuwena iQur’an ukuze sikubangele ubunzima
  20,3,Kepha njengomkhumbuzi kulowo owesaba (uMvelinqangi)
  20,4,Isambulo esivela kulowo owadala umhlaba namazulu aphakeme
  20,5,Onomusa ozinze phezu kwesihlalo sobukhosi
  20,6,Kungokwakhe konke lokho okusemazulwini nakho konke lokho okusemhlabeni nakho konke lokho okuphakathi kwabo kokubili nakho konke lokho okungaphansi komhlaba
  20,7,"Futhi uma ukhuluma ngezwi eliphezulu, ngakho-ke ngempela yena uyayazi imfihlo nokufihlwe ngokwedlulele"
  20,8,"UMvelinqangi, akukho lutho olunokukhonzwa ngaphandle kwakhe, angawakhe amagama amahle ngokwedlulele"
  20,9,Futhi ngakube seyafika yini kuwena indaba kaMose na
  20,10,"Khumbula ngenkathi ebona umlilo ngakho-ke wayesethi kubantu bakhe, “yimani ngempela mina ngibona umlilo, kungenzeka kuthi nginganilethela ilangabi eliphuma kuwona noma ngithole ukuholeka emlilweni”"
  20,11,Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sefika kuwona wamenyezwa (kwathiwa) “Oh Mose!”
  20,12,Ngempela mina ngiyiNkosi yakho ngakho-ke khumula izicathulo zakho ngempela wena usesigodini esingcwele iTuwa
  20,13,Futhi mina ngikukhethile ngakho-ke lalela lokho okuzokwembulwa (kuwena)
  20,14,"Ngempela mina ngingu-Mvelinqangi, akunanto engakhonzwa ngaphandle kwami ngakho-ke ngikhonze futhi wenze umthandazo ukungikhumbula"
  20,15,"Ngempela ihora liyeza, ngiyanqikaza ukulifihla ukuze yonke imiphefumulo ithole umvuzo ngalokho ekuzabalazele"
  20,16,Ngakho-ke ungamvumeli lowo ongakholelwa kulona (ihora) futhi olandela izifiso akuvimbele kulona (ekulilungiseleleni) hleze ubhubhe
  20,17,Futhi yini leyo esesandleni sakho sokudla Oh Mose! na
  20,18,"Wathi (uMose), “induku yami engidondolozela ngayo futhi engehlisela ngayo phansi amaqabunga ezimvu zami futhi ngineminye imisebenzi ngayo”"
  20,19,Wathi (uMvelinqangi) “iphonse phansi Oh Mose!”
  20,20,Ngakho-ke wayiphonsa phansi kwaba ilapho iphenduka khona inyoka ezihambelayo
  20,21,"UMvelinqangi wathi, “ibambe ungesabi sizoyiphindisela esimweni sayo sokuqala”"
  20,22,Futhi cindezela isandla sakho eceleni lakho sizophuma simhlophe singenabubi (lolu) ngolunye uphawu
  20,23,Ukuze sikukhombise ezinye zezimpawu zethu ezinkulu
  20,24,Hamba uye kuFaro ngempela yena akahloniphanga
  20,25,"Wathi (uMose), “Nkosi yami ngivulele isifuba sami”"
  20,26,Futhi ngenzele lula udaba lwami
  20,27,Futhi qaqa ifindo olimini lwami
  20,28,(Ukuze) bayiqonde inkulumo yami
  20,29,Futhi ngiphe umsizi emndenini wami
  20,30,U-Aroni umfowethu
  20,31,Thasisela ngaye emandleni ami
  20,32,Futhi menze ukuthi alekelele odabeni lwami
  20,33,Ukuze sikudumise kakhulu
  20,34,Futhi sikukhumbule kakhulu
  20,35,Ngempela wena ngasosonke isikhathi uyasibona
  20,36,"(UMvelinqangi) wathi, “semukelwe isicelo sakho Oh Mose!”"
  20,37,Futhi ngempela sakwenzela ububele ngenye inkathi
  20,38,Khumbula ngenkathi sembulela unyoko lokho okwembuliwe
  20,39,"Ukuthi ayifake (ingane) ebhokisini bese eliphonsa emfuleni, umfula uzoliphonsa ogwini, siyolithatha (lelo bhokisi) isitha sami nesitha sakhe futhi ngehlisele phezu kwakho uthando oluvela kumina futhi ukuze ukhuliswe ngaphansi kwehlo lami"
  20,40,"Khumbula ngenkathi udadewenu ehamba futhi ethi, “ngakube nginganikhombisa lowo ozomgada yini na?” “Ngakho-ke sakubuyisela kunyoko ukuze apholise amehlo akhe futhi ungaphatheki kabi, ngakho-ke ubulale umuntu sabe sesiyakusindisa enhluphekweni futhi sakulinga ngezilingo wase uhlala iminyaka eminingi nabantu baseMidiyane wabe sewuyeza njengoba kuyisikhathi esinqunyiwe Oh Mose"
  20,41,Futhi ngizikhethele wena
  20,42,Hamba wena nomfowenu namavesi ami futhi nobabili ningadembeseli ekungikhumbuleni
  20,43,HambaninobabiliniyekuFarongempelayenaakahloniphanga
  20,44,"Bese nobabili nikhuluma naye inkulumo emnene, mhlawumbe angakhumbula (anake) noma asabe”"
  20,45,Bathi bobabili (uMose no-Aroni) “Nkosi yethu ngempela thina siyesaba ukuthi hleze ajahise ukusijezisa noma angahloniphi”
  20,46,"(UMvelinqangi) wathi, “nobabili ningesabi ngempela mina ngikanye nani nobabili ngiyezwa futhi ngiyabona”"
  20,47,"Ngakho-ke nobabili hambani niye kuye bese nobabili nithi “ngempela thina sobabili siyizithunywa zeNkosi yakho ngakho-ke bathumele (badedele) kanye nathi abantwana bakwa-Israyeli futhi ungabajezisi, size kuwena nophawu oluphuma eNkosini yakho futhi ukuthula kulowo olandela ukuholwa"
  20,48,Ngempela kwembuliwe kuthina ukuthi isijeziso siyoba phezu kwalowo onqabayo (ophikayo) nofulathelayo
  20,49,"(UFaro) wathi, “Ngakho-ke ngubani iNkosi yenu nobabili Oh Mose! na?”"
  20,50,"(UMose) wathi, “iNkosi yethu yileyo eyanikeza leyo naleyonto ukudalwa kayo yabe seyiyayihola”"
  20,51,"(UFaro) wathi, “kwenzekani ngodaba lwezizukulwane zasendulo na?”"
  20,52,"(UMose) wathi, “ulwazi lwalokho luseNkosini yami, encwadini ayilenzi iphutha iNkosi yami futhi ayikhohlwa”"
  20,53,Iyona eyanenzela umhlaba wandlaleka yabe seyinenzela izindlela zokuhamba kuwona futhi yehlisela phansi amanzi (imvula) eyivela esibhakabhakeni ngakho-ke imvula samilisa ngayo izinhlobonhlobo zezithombo ezingambili
  20,54,Dlanini bese nidedela izinkomo zenu zizidlele ngempela kulokho kunezimpawu kubantu abaqondayo